type name value parameter_list html html_1 (see below) <p>Any valid html can be rendered in the value. This includes the full set of Ionic Components used within the app, e.g.</p> <pre><code>&lt;ion-card&gt;
  &lt;ion-card-header&gt;
    &lt;ion-card-subtitle&gt;Card Subtitle&lt;/ion-card-subtitle&gt;
    &lt;ion-card-title&gt;Card Title&lt;/ion-card-title&gt;
  &lt;/ion-card-header&gt;
  &lt;ion-card-content&gt;
    Keep close to Nature's heart... and break clear away, once in awhile,
    and climb a mountain or spend a week in the woods. Wash your spirit clean.
  &lt;/ion-card-content&gt;
&lt;/ion-card&gt;
</code></pre> <p></p> <p>Google Sheet Demo Live Preview Demo</p>
